mama change your brother's diaper.

1829
01:34:05,645 --> 01:34:07,021
I don't want to go.

1830
01:34:07,105 --> 01:34:08,606
I want to stay and open my presents.

1831
01:34:08,690 --> 01:34:10,275
- All right, come on!
- I don't want to go.

1832
01:34:10,358 --> 01:34:12,193
- I don't care.
- Don't let me tell you twice.

1833
01:34:12,277 --> 01:34:13,862
- Hello.
- Hey, baby.

1834
01:34:14,279 --> 01:34:17,657
Surprise! I came to L.A.
To surprise you.

1835
01:34:17,699 --> 01:34:19,284
