Are you out of your mind?

1836
01:34:19,367 --> 01:34:20,702
I'm with my wife
and my kids.

1837
01:34:20,785 --> 01:34:23,163
Well, on the road,
I'm Mrs. Ray Charles.

1838
01:34:23,204 --> 01:34:24,330
That's on the road.

1839
01:34:24,497 --> 01:34:27,959
Yeah, but, baby, come on,
I got everything set up for us.

1840
