♪ One of these days,
and it won't be long ♪

1847
01:34:50,064 --> 01:34:52,358
♪ You're gonna look for me ♪

1848
01:34:52,442 --> 01:34:55,278
♪ and I'll be gone ♪

1849
01:34:55,361 --> 01:34:56,863
♪ 'Cause I believe ♪

